{"id":8450,"date":"2024-02-09T09:35:20","date_gmt":"2024-02-09T14:35:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=evenement&#038;p=8450"},"modified":"2024-02-09T09:35:33","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T14:35:33","slug":"dejeuner-de-la-perseverance","status":"publish","type":"evenement","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/evenement\/dejeuner-de-la-perseverance\/","title":{"rendered":"D\u00e9jeuner de la pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>\u00c0 l&rsquo;occasion des Journ\u00e9es de la Pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance Scolaire (du 12 au 16 f\u00e9vrier), le c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent organise un d\u00e9jeuner avec distribution de bananes et chocolat chaud.<\/p>\n<p>O\u00f9, quand, comment ? Le lundi 12 f\u00e9vrier d\u00e8s 8 h dans les halls A et E.<\/p>\n<p>En bonus : des petites surprises pour souligner celles et ceux qui pers\u00e9v\u00e8rent&#8230; Soyez l\u00e0, et faites passer le message ! On vous attend.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":8451,"template":"","categorieevenement":[193,2370],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2305,2337,2357],"class_list":["post-8450","evenement","type-evenement","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorieevenement-vie-etudiante","categorieevenement-institutionnel","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-institutionnel","etiquette-interne-reussite-etudiante","etiquette-interne-milieu-de-vie"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:38:28","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"categorieevenement"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement\/8450","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/evenement"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegep